{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 3","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3?lang=deu","contentType":"text/html","pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"896737db6ba64b2c020e92f486404ba60917cb1f","data-aid":"114237820","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3","lang":"deu","data-orig-id":"d8eea313723aec5fb2100222f4e6778642ead1e4","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 3","description":"Älteste ordinieren Priester und Lehrer durch Auflegen der Hände. Um 401–421 n. Chr."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 3","description":"Älteste ordinieren Priester und Lehrer durch Auflegen der Hände. Um 401–421 n. Chr."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"142121307\" id=\"title_number1\">Kapitel 3</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"114237859\" id=\"study_summary1\">Älteste ordinieren Priester und Lehrer durch Auflegen der Hände. Um 401–421 n. Chr.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237860\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Die Art und Weise, wie die Jünger, die die <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Ältesten</a> der Kirche genannt wurden, Priester und Lehrer <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>ordinierten</a>:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237861\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Nachdem sie im Namen Christi zum Vater gebetet hatten, legten sie ihnen die Hände auf und sprachen:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237862\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Im Namen Jesu Christi ordiniere ich dich zum Priester (oder wenn es ein Lehrer sein sollte: ordiniere ich dich zum Lehrer), Umkehr zu predigen und <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Sündenvergebung</a> durch Jesus Christus, durch das Festhalten am Glauben an seinen Namen bis ans Ende. Amen.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237863\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>Und auf diese Art und Weise <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>ordinierten</a> sie Priester und Lehrer gemäß den <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>Gaben</a> und Berufungen, die Gott den Menschen gibt; und sie ordinierten sie durch die <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>Macht</a> des Heiligen Geistes, die in ihnen war.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237864\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=deu#p1\">Al 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Ältester</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237865\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Ordinieren, Ordinierung</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237866\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Vergebung der Sünden</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237867\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=deu#p32\">LuB 18:32</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=deu#p60\">20:60</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237868\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Gabe</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237869\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=deu#p37\">1 Ne 13:37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=deu#p9\">Moro 6:9</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"114237860","context":"Ältesten","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237864\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=deu#p1\">Al 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Ältester</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=deu#p1","text":"Al 6:1"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=deu","text":"SF Ältester"}]},"note1b":{"id":"note1b","marker":"1b","pid":"114237860","context":"ordinierten","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237865\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Ordinieren, Ordinierung</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=deu","text":"SF Ordinieren, Ordinierung"}]},"note3a":{"id":"note3a","marker":"3a","pid":"114237862","context":"Sündenvergebung","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237866\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Vergebung der Sünden</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=deu","text":"SF Vergebung der Sünden"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"114237863","context":"ordinierten","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237867\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=deu#p32\">LuB 18:32</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=deu#p60\">20:60</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=deu#p32","text":"LuB 18:32"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=deu#p60","text":"20:60"}]},"note4b":{"id":"note4b","marker":"4b","pid":"114237863","context":"Gaben","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237868\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Gabe</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=deu","text":"SF Gabe"}]},"note4c":{"id":"note4c","marker":"4c","pid":"114237863","context":"Macht","text":"<p data-aid=\"114237869\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=deu#p37\">1 Ne 13:37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=deu#p9\">Moro 6:9</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=deu#p37","text":"1 Ne 13:37"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=deu#p9","text":"Moro 6:9"}]}}},"pids":[["114237820",{"key":"114237820"}],["142121307",{"key":"142121307"}],["114237859",{"key":"114237859"}],["114237860",{"key":"114237860"}],["114237861",{"key":"114237861"}],["114237862",{"key":"114237862"}],["114237863",{"key":"114237863"}],["114237864",{"key":"114237864"}],["114237865",{"key":"114237865"}],["114237866",{"key":"114237866"}],["114237867",{"key":"114237867"}],["114237868",{"key":"114237868"}],["114237869",{"key":"114237869"}]]